subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Ted Schulz won the First Tee Open for his first Champions Tour title, holing a 12-foot birdie putt on the 17th hole at Pebble Beach en route to a two-under 70 and a one-shot victory over Tom Pernice Jr.
